OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and rain spread
OL,6,Fnortheastwards this morning. A
OL,7,Fbrighter and breezier spell develops
OL,8,Ffor a time during the afternoon, but
OL,9,Fshowers or longer spells of rain
OL,10,Ffollow with a risk of isolated
OL,11,Fthunderstorms.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain and showers slowly
OL,14,Ffading away with skies largely
OL,15,Fclearing during the second half of the
OL,16,Fnight. Winds strengthening overnight,
OL,17,Fparticularly towards the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
